snippet.title: Skateboard Madness Xtreme Edition (PS2 Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Skateboard Madness Xtreme Edition takes you around the globe and gives you the opportunity to show everyone that a new skateboarding legend has been born, and not just any old legend, the greatest of all time. 
Ever dreamed of traveling the globe's skateboarding events? Can you pull off the most amazing and dare-devil tricks? Can you land the infamous 1080 and ride with the big boys? 
Find out in Skateboard Madness Xtreme Edition now...
